{"tid":187223,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)逃獄三王","createTime":"2017-04-04T19:26:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-04T20:23:20.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"705fc77755a6ed44e3dccf80f045ad4f5405f672","tid":187223,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T19:26:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=nNI0xXmu%2FnmsXsjxjv7MVaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=a242402e\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> 按右上主頁可以睇返V台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=nNI0xXmu%2FnmsXsjxjv7MVaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=347d0db7\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/5/5b/O_brother_where_art_thou_ver1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F5%2F5b%2FO_brother_where_art_thou_ver1.jpg&h=0aed7b61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n30年代初，密西西比州荒野的監獄裡，一群&ldquo;勞改犯&rdquo;正乾著枯燥，繁重的採石，碎石的活計嘮嘮叨叨，油嘴滑舌的艾弗瑞特（喬治&middot;克魯尼飾）也是其中 在一個破壞石頭上，整天打著各種逃跑的鬼主意。在成功說服了難點頭腦簡單的德爾瑪（蒂姆&middot;布雷克&middot;尼爾森飾）和相當 大膽的皮特（約翰&middot;特托羅飾）之後，艾弗瑞特的越獄大計終於得以實現，三個穿著犯人服，拖著手銬，腳鐐的罪叮叮叮噹當地踏上了通往自由和寶藏的路途<br />\n<br />\n3 20AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6fb7f4f0eb7e402aa38f710c570410d4f4aa1fd","tid":187223,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T19:51:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84df6965236b528328e92a34c